content: I wake up at 7 am on weekdays. My work hours are 9 am to 5 pm. I aim to get 7-8 hours of sleep each night. My top three priorities are exercise, meal prep, and focused work hours. I'd like to dedicate about an hour to meal prep each day. Oh, and by the way, I've been having oatmeal with banana and honey for breakfast on certain days of the week, but I'm open to new ideas.
